***************
*** 118,124
  .P
  The type \&\f5seek_dir\fP\& is a synonym for an integer type
  (indicated here as \&\f6T3\fP\&) that permits certain member functions to
! overload others on parameters of type \&\f5iostate\fP\& and provide the
  same behavior.
  .P
  .ix "[streamoff]"

